code: /**  * Resolve the given request to a list of media types. The returned list is  * ordered by specificity first and by quality parameter second.  * @param webRequest the current request  * @return the requested media types, or {@link #MEDIA_TYPE_ALL_LIST} if none  * were requested.  * @throws HttpMediaTypeNotAcceptableException if the requested media  * types cannot be parsed  */ List<MediaType> resolveMediaTypes(NativeWebRequest webRequest) throws HttpMediaTypeNotAcceptableException.
